data.description: Stunning 3 Bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage Home in southwest Fort Worth!  This home features a nice size living area with a view from a nice size kitchen with a breakfast bar.  The primary suite is very cozy with a peaceful garden tube to help you relax after a stressful day, the suite also has a separate shower and a huge walk-in closet.  The other 2 bedrooms are nice size.  The backyard is very large for BBQ's and entertaining.  This Home is jewel and waiting for the perfect Buyer to come purchase it.
